      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Clean, honest good-condition vehicle that runs and drives well. It shows normal light wear for its age and use, but overall it presents nicely inside and out and feels like a car that has been kept up better than average. Expect a solid driver with a respectable interior, good overall appearance, and the usual minor cosmetic signs of use rather than anything major. This is not a brand-new car, but for a used vehicle in this condition, buyers can expect a dependable, well-kept example.",
