    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left to give? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transport, a project to tinker with, or a handy extra vehicle. It\u2019s been represented honestly and priced fairly, and for the right buyer it offers a lot of value without breaking the bank. If you want something straightforward, usable, and easy on the wallet, this one is worth a look.",
