      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Tough, honest driver with solid bones and plenty of mechanical character. Starts up, runs, and delivers a connected, old-school feel with a powertrain that still pulls cleanly and a chassis that remains composed where it counts. Not a showpiece, but a capable project, budget commuter, or weekend wrench-turner with usable road manners and straightforward mechanicals. Ideal for someone who wants an affordable car with potential rather than over-restored fluff. Priced to move and worth a look for the right buyer.",
